info.name: EIA APIv2
info.description: Swagger UI interface for EIA's APIv2.  You can also explore EIA's API using the [Opendata Query Browser](https://www.eia.gov/opendata/browser/).  For this UI, you must use your EIA `api key` to apply filters and return data. You can register for an API Key at [https://www.eia.gov/opendata/](https://www.eia.gov/opendata/)
